title: Funko Debuts New Walgreen Exclusive WWE And DC POPs
text:
Funko Debuts New Walgreen Exclusive WWE And DC POPs Matthew Mueller Start Slideshow Slide of 
In the ongoing search for exclusive Funko products, fans can expect to find a few new options at their local Walgreens over the next few months. 
Previous Walgreen exclusives have included Kamala Khan, Green Goblin, a Star Wars: Episode VII - The Force Awakens Rey variant, Unmasked Spider-Gwen, PloKoon, and Kit Fisto, and admittedly the choices have skewed more towards Marvel and Star Wars. 
Funko is expanding their Walgreens exclusives for this latest batch and will include a selection of WWE and DC Comics-inspired releases. From the WWE side comes the Heartbreak Kid Shawn Michaels and the big red monster Kane. For DC, fans can get ahold of John Stewart and a Black Suit Joker. 
You'll start seeing these POPs show up in Walgreens locations this February, so hit the next slide to check out the new exclusive up close!
